messages.message: @Travis @Franklin Chian I think this (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/34833) should fix the poetry issues youâ€™ve been seeing, rebase on top of the latest master and then run `make update-python` again in any services that are down. if you get a permission error, run `poetry env info --path` to get the path to the venv, then `sudo rm -rf <venv-path>`  to force-remove it and then `make update-python` to build it again. let me know if it works or if you run into any other issues, thanks for helping troubleshoot the upgrade!
